Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongereye cyane mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika n'ubumwe bw'ubukungu (European Economic Area) n'u Bwongereza, kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza imyitwarire isa n'iy'ibihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri ku rugero rutandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye, kigenda gihita gitera imbere ku isi hose.
Mu rwego rw'igihugu, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bikennye cyane bigomba kurushaho kwitegura umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, abantu barwaye indwara ya Pneumonia itaramenyekana yaturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko iyi ndwara yatewe na coronavirus itaramenyekana, ubu izwi nka coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, icyorezo cyatewe n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyiswe coronavirus disease (COVID-19).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko abagera kuri 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 baba bafite uburwayi buto, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'inzira yo mu mwuka bufite cyangwa butagira ingwara ya filimi, kandi abenshi muri bo bakira.
Mu bice 14%, COVID-19 iba indwara ikomeye cyane igasaba ko umuntu ashyirwa mu buriri, naho 6% by'abaturage bagakira cyane bagasaba ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Abarwayi bashyizwe mu buriri kubera COVID-19 bapfa bagera kuri 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'ubukungu (EU/EEA) no mu Burayi (Ubwongereza) ugereranyije n'uwa Hubei Province, mu Bushinwa.
Nanone, dugereranya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri iki gihe mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cyo ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu ndetse n'imyifatire y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'Isi ikurikira iy'iki gihugu.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Mu kiganiro cya Eurosurveillance 2020 cyo ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe, Spiteri na bagenzi be bavuze ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ba mbere mu Burayi nk'uko WHO ibivuga.
Mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA, abantu ba mbere banduye mu Bufaransa ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020 ubwo abo bantu bari bavuye i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yari imaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, aho hagati ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'uwo munsi w'irondakoko, abantu 39,768 barwaye n'abo bapfuye 1,727, mu gihe abarwayi 17,750 n'abapfuye 1,441 bari mu Butaliyani gusa.
Umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'abanduye COVID-19 ugenda wiyongera
Mu Kigo cy'Igihugu cy'Igihugu cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Gukurikirana no Gukurikirana Indwara z'Ibiza (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose ku isi, hakoreshejwe imbuga nkoranyambaga z'inzego nka Minisiteri y'Ubuzima mu bihugu by'amahanga, ibiro by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Gishinzwe Ubuzima n'Igihugu (WHO) n'ibindi, bishyurwa buri munsi saa mbiri za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma ibipimo bya COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, agereranywa n'ibyo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko tubikesha Ibaruramari ry'abanduye COVID-19 bakivurwa, twagerageje kugenzura umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bagaragaye mu minsi 14, mu bihugu byose bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twagaragaje kandi ko umubare w'abanduye mu gihugu cyose uzagenda wiyongera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa mbiri za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'uwavuzwe mu Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama.
Imyitwarire ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bagaragaye mu minsi 14 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange ukurikije imibare y'Intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Ifoto 1).
Mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma ugera ku gipimo cya nyuma cy'abazavuka ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ukuboza).
Ibi byatewe n'umubare w'abantu baguye muri COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane uvuye mu Butaliyani, ariko kimwe n'ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA ndetse n'u Bwongereza, hari n'umubare w'abantu baguye muri COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane (Kokoro).
Mu ishusho ya 2 hagaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19, mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama15 Werurwe 2020.
Ivuga ko ku itariki ya 15 Kanama saa mbiri za mu gitondo, ibihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza byari bifite umubare w'abanduye ungana n'uwavuzwe mu Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 gusa cyangwa birenga.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibipimo by'abantu banduye COVID-19 bigaragaza ko iki cyorezo kigenda cyongerekana mu bihugu byose.
Ibi bikomeza bityo nubwo ibihugu bifite uburyo bwo kwivuza buri ku rwego rumwe, ibipimo bitandukanye byo kumenya umuntu urwaye ndetse n'ingamba zitandukanye zo gufata abantu bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bagaragaze ko bafite COVID-19, harimo no kongera umubare w'abageragezwa.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twatewe n'ibiza mu Butaliyani basobanuye ko 10% by'abanduye COVID-19 bari bakeneye ubuvuzi bukomeye kandi amakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye muri utwo turere byari byuzuye.
Ibimenyetso by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro no/cyangwa mu cyumba cy'ubuvuzi bukomeye bigera ku kigero cya EU/EEA ni 6% na 1% gusa, (ibi byerekana ko nta makuru ahari).
Ahubwo, ibyo bigomba gutangwa mu buryo buhuje n'amakuru agaragaza umubare w'abarwayi bapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko uburebure bw'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bukomeye n'iby'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze mu Burayi, mu Budage hari ibitanda 29.2 naho muri Porutugali hari ibitanda 4.2 ku bantu 100.000.
Ibi bivuze ko hari ibihugu bifite ubuvuzi buhagije cyangwa budahagije nk'ubwo mu Butaliyani (ibitanda 12.5 by'uburwayi bw'ikirenga ku bantu 100.000 mu 201011).
Ingaruka z'ibanze ku buryo ibikoresho by'ubuzima bigezweho byiyongera, zishingiye ku kugereranya abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu buriri mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza hamwe n'ikibazo cy'uko umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu buriri mu buriri bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, hamwe n'uko umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu buriri bw'uburwayi bw'umubiri wiyongereyeho 90% mu gihe bari mu buriri bw'uburwayi, byavuzwe mu raporo ya gatandatu ya ECDC yihuta ku kigero cy'akaga cya COVID-19.
