Ku bw'ibyo, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bikeneye kwitegura ko SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira mu baturage bo mu turere dutandukanye, kandi ko umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ukomeza kwiyongera, cyane cyane mu duce tw'Ubutaliyani tudafite uburwayi.
Nkuko byagaragajwe n'igenzura rikomeye rya ECDC, gutegura neza vuba ni ngombwa mu gukumira ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, ndetse no mu guhita uhita uhita uhita uhita uhita uhita uhita uhita uhita uhita utera, kuko kwiyongera byihuse kw'umubare w'abarwayi wifuza bishobora gutuma abayobozi n'ibitaro badahabwa igihe gihagije cyo kumenya, kwemera no gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bukenewe mu gihe byaba bitakozwe hakiri kare.
Gusuzuma ibibazo byihutirwa bigaragaza uburyo bwo kwivuza bwo kurwanya iki kibazo.
Hariho ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi ibihugu bifite ubushobozi bwo kongera imbaraga mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ingufu mu by'ubuvuzi.
Iyo ibyo bitagenze neza, byitezwe ko ibigo by'ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA bizajya bihatirwa kubera umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bukomeye mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyateje indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), cyahitanye abantu barenga 3,000 kandi abantu barenga 80,000 bakaba bamaze kwandura mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu, bituma abantu bagerwaho n'akaga.
Nk'uko bimeze ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV, cyateye SARS mu bihumbi by'abantu mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na yo ishobora kwandura indwara z'ibicurane kandi igatanga ibimenyetso bimwe na bimwe.
Ariko kandi, COVID-19 ntabwo ari yo SARS ikunda cyane kandi ihitana abantu bake cyane ariko ikwirakwira cyane kandi ikagira ingaruka ku bagabo n'abagabo bakuze kurusha urubyiruko n'abagore.
Mu gusubiza ibitabo byinshi byatangaje iby'iyo ndwara, iyi gazeti igamije kugaragaza ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku byerekeye iyo ndwara.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze byerekeye indwara, icyayiteza, virusi, uburyo bwo kugenzura, uburyo bwo kuvura, kumenya iby'igihe kizaza n'uburyo bwo kuzirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko ibyo twasuzumye bizadufasha gusobanukirwa no gukemura icyo kibazo cy'indwara itera impungenge abantu.
Umunsi mukuru w'Icyunamo wo ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cy'ikiruhuko cyose ndetse no mu byumweru bikurikiyeho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara ya virusi itera SIDA itari yamenyekanye.
Iyi virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ni yo mpamvu iyi virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 yavuye ku ndwara ya SARS (Sindrome respiratoire aiguë sévère) mu mwaka wa 2003; ku bw'ibyo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryayihinduye izina SARS-CoV-2 ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi icyorezo cyayo cyiswe CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze vuba aha cyakwirakwira mu gihugu hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi.
Ku itariki ya 2 Kanama 2020, virusi ya COVID-19 yari imaze gutuma abantu barenga 80,000 bagerwaho n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abagera ku 40.000 bakize naho abagera ku 3.000 bahitanwa n'icyo cyorezo.
OMS iragabisha ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi wa 1 w'abantu kandi ko ishobora guteza akaga kurusha iterabwoba.
Nkuko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, hasohotse impapuro zisaga 200 zivuga kuri COVID-19 zirimo icyorezo, indwara, icyateye, ikigeragezo n'ubuvuzi kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragaje ko virusi ya i yakomotse ku bantu batandukanye.
Iki gikorwa cyo gushakisha kiri mu rwego rwo kwigana ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri iki kibuga gishya cy'umupira w'amaguru.
Mu ntangiriro, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, indwara yo mu mutwe yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, 2012).
Nanone turi busuzume ibyo twize ku birebana n'uko twakwirinda indwara z'uburwayi, ibyo abantu batekereza ko ari ukuri n'ibibazo by'ingenzi tudashoboye gusubiza.
Iyo virusi ya CoV yabonwaga ko ari virusi idafite ubukana ku bantu, ikaba ari yo ituma abantu bagera kuri 15% bahura n'indwara ya grippe 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twabonye ko COVID-19 ari virusi ebyiri z'ubwandu, ari yo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatangiye kwandura mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, zigasakara mu bindi bihugu vuba, zikaba zaranduye abantu benshi.
Bityo rero, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu ishusho. Ishusho.1,1, abarwayi ba malariya batigeze bamenyekana ku isoko ryabo babanje kumenyekana i Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kuri Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu y'u Bushinwa.
