Ku wa kane, Bangladesh yemeje ko abandi bantu batanu bapfuye bazize COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Ni umubare munini cyane w'abapfuye ku munsi umwe bazize iyi virusi.
Ku mugoroba w'uyu munsi, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'ubushakashatsi (IEDCR) cyanditse abantu 114 barwaye indwara z'indwara, 33 bakize bari mu rugo.
Abantu bose hamwe ni 17.
Mu makuru yo kuri interineti, umuyobozi mukuru wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko mu bapfuye harimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dukurikije uko Dr Meerjady abivuga, babiri mu bapfuye bari bafite imyaka isaga 60, babiri bari bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 51 na 60, undi akaba yari afite imyaka iri hagati ya 41 na 50.
Yavuze ko babiri muri bo bari baturutse i Dhaka.
