Umuntu wa mbere wanduye coronavirus utaramenyekana, yanduye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe gusa, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wazamutse buhoro buhoro.
Aba bantu bari bafitanye isano n'isoko ry'amafi ryo mu mugi wa Huanan (Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market), ryatangaga amatungo mazima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yavuye kuri imwe muri izo nyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ko ikomoka ku nyamaswa.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bya Wuhan Central Hospital ryemeje ko hari virusi ifitanye isano na "SARS coronavirus".
Abaganga umunani, barimo Li Wenliang, bashinjwa n'abapolisi ko bakwirakwiza ibinyoma, naho undi witwa Ai Fen ashinjwa n'abakoresha be ko bakubita abantu.
Ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya Wuhan Municipal Health Commission cyatanze itangazo ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, cyamenyesha OMS.
Abategetsi b'i Wuhan bari bamaze kubwira abarwayi batari bazi niba bari bafite virusi itera SIDA ko bagombaga gutangira gukora ubushakashatsi mu ntangiriro za Mutarama.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi ya Virusi ya Corona yageze mu bindi bice by'u Bushinwa, ibi bikaba byatewe n'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'u Bushinwa ndetse n'aho Wuhan ari umujyi w'imodoka nyinshi n'aho gari ya moshi ziva.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje ko bwabonye abarwayi bashya bagera ku 140 mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri i Beijing n'undi umwe i Shenzhen.
Nyuma, amakuru yemewe agaragaza ko abantu 6.174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020; ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yashyize Ubushinwa ku rutonde rw'abanduye ku isi; ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu basaga 1.61 bari bamaze kugaragara ku isi; abantu basaga 97,000 bari barapfuye naho 364,000 bakize.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 n'ibihugu bitandukanye byamaze kubona nibura umuntu umwe urwaye.
Mu bihugu byinshi byo mu Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen bibuza abantu kujya mu bihugu byabo kandi bigashyiraho imipaka igabanyijemo imbibi.
Bimwe mu bihugu byashyizeho gahunda zo kwirinda ikwirakwira harimo icyorezo cya Corona (cyitwa ko cyitwa Guma mu rugo, cyitwa Guma mu rugo cyangwa cyitwa Guma mu rugo) n'icyorezo cy'indwara. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 300, cyangwa 90% by'abaturage bose bari mu cyiciro kimwe cy'indwara muri Amerika, abantu barenga miriyoni 50 bari mu cyiciro cy'indwara muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 59 bari mu cyiciro cy'indwara muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu miriyoni 1.3 bari mu cyiciro cy'indwara mu Buhindi.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu bagera kuri miriyari 1.7 bari mu mibabaro y'ubwoko butandukanye, kandi nyuma y'iminsi ibiri umubare w'abantu bari mu mibabaro wariyongereye ugera kuri miriyari 2.6 - ni ukuvuga kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 byitezwe ko yabonetse ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; hari raporo imwe yemewe igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 yabonetse ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jixian yagaragaje itsinda ry'abarwayi bataramenyekana ry'indwara ya SIDA yamuzanye ku wa 26 Ukuboza, nyuma yaho ibitaro by'i Wuhan byatangaje abayobozi ba Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku wa 27 Ukuboza.
Igerageza rya mbere ry'ubwoko bw'abarwayi ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 ryagaragaje ko bafite virusi ya coronavirus isa na SARS.
Itangazo ry'abaturage ryashyizwe ahagaragara n'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya Wuhan Municipal Health Commission ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
Ibyo byamenyeshejwe OMS ku munsi umwe.
Ubwo ubwo butumwa bwageragaho, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan baburiwe n'igipolisi ko bagiye gukwirakwiza amakuru y'icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu y'u Bushinwa mu ntangiriro yavuze ko nta "bimenyetso byumvikana" bigaragaza ko indwara zandurira ku muntu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'u Bushinwa yatangije gahunda ikomeye cyane yashyizweho n'Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping, yise "intambara y'abaturage" yo kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi.
Mu gihe cyiswe "Kwihererana ku Isi" mu buzima bw'umuntu, ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko guhagarika ingendo zo kujya i Wuhan cyangwa kuva i Wuhan, kandi byongerewe mu mijyi 15 yo muri Hubei, bigira ingaruka ku baturage bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Mu mijyi ntibiremewe gukoresha imodoka za bwite.
Imirimo yo kwizihiza Umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (25 Mutarama) yahagaritswe mu duce dutandukanye.
Nanone abategetsi batangaje ko hubatswe ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, bikaba byarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hari undi bitaro byubatswe, bitwaga Leishenshan Hospital, kugira ngo bivurire abandi barwayi.
Uretse ibitaro byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bibanza 14 i Wuhan, urugero nk'ibibuga by'inama n'ibibuga by'umupira w'amaguru n'ibigo by'ibitaro by'agateganyo.Ku wa 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho andi mabwiriza yo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo n'ibyangombwa by'abitabiriye urugendo bavuga uko ubuzima bwabo bwifashe n'uko bagiye kongera iminsi mikuru yo mu Rwibutso.
Kaminuza n'amashuri yo hirya no hino mu gihugu na byo byarahagaritswe.
Hong Kong na Macau byashyizeho amategeko menshi, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri ya kaminuza.
Mu Bushinwa hari ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho gahunda yo gukora akazi.
Imirimo yo kwimuka yari ihagaritswe mu karere ka Hubei no hanze yarwo.
Imikorere y'abagenzi yarahindutse, kandi ahantu hahurira abantu benshi mu rwego rw'ubukerarugendo hafunzwe.
Mu mijyi myinshi, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (benshi mu baturage bose) bageragejweho ingendo z'abantu. Igihe icyorezo cyakwirakwiraga ku isi hose muri Werurwe, abategetsi bo mu Bushinwa bashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zo kurwanya virusi no kuyimura mu mahanga.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo kwirinda ubwandu ku banyamahanga bose binjira mu Bushinwa. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa hari umuntu umwe gusa wari umaze iminsi itanu arwaye kandi akaba yari umujyanama wari wasubiye i Guangzhou avuye i Istanbul.
Ku itariki ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo mu Bushinwa ryagaragaye ko ridafite aho rihuriye n'icyorezo cy'indwara muri icyo gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, ibihano byo guhagarika ingendo byongeye gufatirwa muri Hubei, uretse i Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri byamaze byashyiriweho.Ministry of Foreign Affairs y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ku wa 26 Werurwe 2020 ko visa zo kwinjira mu Bushinwa cyangwa uruhushya rwo gukora mu Bushinwa bizagoreka guhera ku wa 28 Werurwe, ndetse n'ibindi bitaramenyekana igihe itegeko rizaburanira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bazajya basabwa gusaba viza ku biro by'u Bushinwa.
