COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020 avuye mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'igihugu ryita ku buzima ryavuze ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habayeho ukwiyongera kw'abarwayi, bivugwa ko byatewe n'inama y'idini rishya ryitwa Shincheonji Church of Jesus yabereye i Daegu.
Abari mu idini rya Shincheonji bari baje i Daegu bavuye i Wuhan, ni bo bagaragaye ko ari bo bateje imbere icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bantu 9.336, 1.261 cyangwa ibice hafi 13% by'abari bagize itorero, bavugaga ko bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko hari umuburo ukomeye kurushaho ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, muri Koreya habonetse abarwayi basaga 2.000, maze ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare habonetse abarwayi 3.150.
Inzu zose za gisirikare zo muri Koreya y'Epfo zashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bagaragajwe ko bafite virusi.
Imirimo yo gutwara indege nayo yarahindutse, bityo ihinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yafashwe nk'iy'ubwoko bunini kandi bwiza ku isi yo kuvana abantu banduye, gushyira ku ruhande abantu bose banduye, bakurikirana no gushyira mu kato umuntu wese wagize icyo ahura na virusi.
Uburyo bwo kwishyura bwari bufite uburyo bwo kwishyura ibipimo by'abimukira bavuye mu mahanga bakoresheje porogaramu za telefoni, gutwara imodoka bajya ku cyumba cyo gupima virusi ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 20,000 ku munsi.
Gahunda ya Koreya y'Epfo yafashwe nk'igikorwa cyatsinze mu kurwanya icyorezo nubwo imijyi yose itari mu kato.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko basaba Moon kuva ku butegetsi bavuga ko leta ititaye ku ndwara y'ibicurane, abandi bakabihakana.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yari imaze ibyumweru bine ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku isi.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abagenzi bose bavuye mu bindi bihugu bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 1 Mata, ibinyamakuru byatangaje ko Koreya y'Epfo yasabye ibihugu 121 inkunga yo gukoresha ibikoresho byo gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje ko hari umuntu wa mbere wanduye SARS-CoV-2 ku wa 19 Gashyantare i Qom, kandi Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi yatangaje ko abantu babiri bapfuye kuri uwo munsi.
Mu bikorwa bya mbere leta yatangaje harimo gutangiza ibitaramo n'ibirori by'umuco, imyidagaduro, gusenga kuwa gatanu, gufunga za kaminuza, amashuri yisumbuye n'amashuri.
Irani yashyizeho miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda kugira ngo irwanye virusi.
Ku itariki ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato abantu bo mu turere twari twarangiritse, kandi ko abantu bagomba gushyirwa mu kato.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, hatangajwe gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo z'abantu benshi mu mijyi, nubwo ingendo nyinshi zo mu minsi mikuru y'Umwaka mushya w'Ubuperesi (Persian New Year Nowruz) zakomeje.
Ibibanza by'amasengesho by'Abashiya i Qom byafunguwe ku basenga Imana kugeza ku wa 16 Werurwe 2020. Irani yabaye icyicaro cy'ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera SIDA mu gihe cy'ihindukira ry'u Bushinwa mu kwezi kwa kabiri.
Mu gihe ibihugu birenga icumi byemezaga ko hari icyorezo cya Coronavirus muri Irani, byatangaje ko abantu 388 bari muri Irani ku wa 28 Gashyantare, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo cyari gikomeye kurusha abarwayi 388 Leta ya Irani yari yatangaje ko bari muri icyo gihugu ku wa 28 Gashyantare.
Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yahagaritswe, kuko ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, abanyamuryango 23 muri 290 bari bamaze gupimwa basanga bafite virusi.
Ku itariki ya 12 Gashyantare, umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu (Human Rights Watch) wasabye abayobozi ba gereza zo muri Irani kurekura abantu bose baharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu kandi bakabarekura igihe runaka.
Hari amakuru avuga ko icyorezo cya Virusi ya Corona gishobora gukwirakwira mu duce duturanye, urugero nk'i Jakarta, aho nta buvuzi buhagije buhari.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, bakaba ari bo bantu benshi cyane muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abayobozi 12 ba Irani n'abandi bayobozi b'igihugu bari barapfuye bazize icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari imaze kubona abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha, kandi umuntu umwe yapfaga buri minota icumi kubera coronavirus.
Umukozi wa OMS avuga ko umubare w'abarwayi muri Irani ushobora kuba wikubye inshuro eshanu uw'abavugwa mu rurimi rw'icyongereza.
Hari kandi igitekerezo cy'uko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora gutuma igihugu cy'icyo gihugu kitamenya uko kihangana n'icyo cyorezo.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku burenganzira bwa muntu (UN High Commissioner for Human Rights) wasabye ibihugu byibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Iran, ko byishyura amafaranga menshi.
Icyorezo cy'indwara cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama, ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezwaga bagasanga bafite SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Umubare w'abanduye watangiye kwiyongera cyane ku buryo leta y'u Butaliyani yahagaritse ingendo zose z'indege ziva mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko hashize igihe gito.
Icyorezo cy'indwara idashingiye kuri COVID-19 cyasuzumwe nyuma, gitangira ku bantu 16 bemejwe ko banduye mu ntara ya Lombardy ku wa 21 Gashyantare.Ku wa 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo kurwanya icyorezo, harimo gushyira abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu Ntara zo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani mu kato.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "mu turere tw'ibihe bidasanzwe, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizemewe.
Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yatangaje ko amashuri n'amayunivesite yose yo mu gihugu hose azafungwa burundu, mu gihe icyo gihe u Butaliyani bwari bwaramaze guhitana abantu 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo imikino ya shampiyona y'umupira w'amaguru (Serie A football matches), yagombaga gukinwa mu mazu kugeza ku itariki ya 1 Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri Conte yatangaje ko ibikorwa hafi ya byose by'ubucuruzi bihagaritswe uretse ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ananesthesiya, Analgesia, Resuscitation and Intensive Care (SIAARTI) cyasohoye amabwiriza ku bijyanye n'imihango yo gupima indwara z'indwara (trial protocols) ishobora gukoreshwa mu bushakashatsi.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwashyize Ubushinwa ku rutonde rw'abapfuye ku isi bose bahitanywe na coronavirus ubwo bwavugaga ko hari abantu 3,405 bapfuye bazize icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko u Burusiya bwari bwarashyize indege icyenda z'intambara mu Butaliyani.
Ku itariki ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128.948 banduye, 15.887 bapfuye, 21.815 barakira, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
CNN yatangaje ko kuba u Butaliyani bufite abasaza benshi cyane ku buryo butabasha gupima abantu bose bafite icyorezo cya SIDA, bishobora gutuma umubare w'abapfa wiyongera.
Uburyo bwo kuvura bwa mbere bw'iki cyorezo mu Bwongereza bwagaragaye ko ari bwo bworoheje kurusha ubundi mu bihugu byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo, kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'u Bwongereza ntiyari yarashyizeho itegeko ryo guha abaturage ubwirinzi cyangwa kwikinga mu rwego rw'isi yose.
Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko yagiriye inama abaturage kwirinda ingendo zidakwiriye no guhuza n'abandi, avuga ko igihe cyose bishoboka bagomba gukora imirimo yo mu rugo kandi bakirinda ahantu nk'amabarubari, ibibuga by'imikino n'aho baba.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro, urugero nk'amabariro n'amazu y'ibyishimo, byari gufungwa vuba uko bishoboka kose, kandi isezeranya ko izishyura 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi ku kigero cya £2,500 buri kwezi kugira ngo birinde kubura akazi muri iki gihe cy'akaga. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje gahunda z'igihe kirekire, ashyiriraho abantu benshi cyane, kandi abuza abantu kujya mu materaniro menshi no gukora imirimo yo hanze y'inzu igihe cyose bibaye ngombwa.
Uretse ibikorwa by'ibanze byashyizweho, polisi yari ihagaritse ko ibyo bihano byashyirwa mu bikorwa, kandi ko amateraniro yose yabaga ahagaritswe.
Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwasabwe gufunga uretse ubushinjacyaha bw'ubucuruzi bwemewe n'amategeko, harimo ibigo by'ubucuruzi, ibigo by'ubuvuzi, banki, ibigo by'ibikomoka ku mavuta, ibigo by'amavuta n'amagaraji.
Tariki ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 wabonetse muri leta ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika yari umugabo wasubiye mu gihugu avuye i Wuhan ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama.
Ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus cyiswe White House Coronavirus Task Force cyashinzwe ku itariki ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama, ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari gahunda y'ubuzima mu gihugu kandi bugashyiraho ibihano ku bavuye mu Bushinwa.
