Umunsi umwe Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku Itegeko rivuga ku bijyanye no gutanga inkunga y'inyongera ku bijyanye no kwitegura no gusubiza Coronavirus (Coronavirus Preparedness and Response Supplemental Appropriations Act) ryatumye leta z'ibihugu by'ibihumbi 8 n'ibihumbi 300 z'amadolari y'Amerika zitanga inkunga yo kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Amashami yashyizeho amategeko abuzanya abakozi, ategeka ko batagomba gukora mu rugo, kandi ababwiriza b'uturere batangiraga gukora mu rugo.
Imikino n'imikino byari biteganyijwe byarahagaritswe.Ku wa 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko ibihano byo kujya mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, uretse mu Bwongereza, bizamara iminsi 30, guhera ku wa 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yaguye amategeko y'ubwami yongeraho n'ay'u Bwongereza na Irilande.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko hari igihe cy'amahoro mu gihugu hose, cyatumye amafaranga ya leta akoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi byafunze cyangwa bigabanyiriza amasaha yo gukora muri Amerika yose mu rwego rwo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyaramaze kwemezwa mu majyaruguru 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko mu mujyi wa New York hari abantu 10.700 banduye coronavirus, bakaba baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku itariki ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko igihe cyo kwihagarika gisa n'aho ari cyiza kuko umubare w'abarwayi wiyongereye ugenda ugabanuka, uva ku minsi 2.0 ugera ku minsi 4.7.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, mu mugi wa New York hari abantu 32.308 banduye, abantu 672 bakaba barapfuye bazize virusi itera SIDA. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yari ifite umubare munini w'abanduye kurusha indi migi yose ku isi, hakubiyemo u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, muri Amerika hari abantu 400,335 banduye, abantu 12.841 bakaba barapfuye.
Amakuru ya Per media yo ku wa 30 Werurwe yatangaje ko Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera igihe cy'ibihano by'impunzi kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Umunsi umwe, ibitaro byo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika (USNS Comfort), bikoresha ubwato bw'ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, byashyize i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, Amerika yari imaze guhitana abantu 884 kubera coronavirus mu masaha 24 gusa.
Mu mujyi wa New York, abarwayi barenga 100,000 ku itariki ya 3 Mata, ibiro by'ibiro by'ishami by'abaperezida byashyizwe ahagaragara kubera ko byamagana ko ibibazo byo gucunga amakuru ya rusange ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi, bigatuma abahanga mu by'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi batanga amakuru yose n'inyandiko byasohotse mu biro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Muri rusange, uburyo Trump yakoresheje iyi nkuru bwagaragajwe cyane mu buryo bw'igitekerezo cyo kwiyahura.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika n'abanyamakuru bavuze ko Amerika ikomeje kwishingikiriza ku bucuruzi bw'ibikomoka ku ngufu, harimo n'imiti yo mu Bushinwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku birebana n'urugendo rw'ikirere, bwagaragaje ko indwara zikwirakwira, bwasohotse mu kinyamakuru cyitwa The Journal of Travel Medicine hagati muri Mutarama 2020.
Raporo yo mu 2018 yatanzwe n'Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Urukiko Rushinzwe Ubwogero bw'Ibirere (International Air Transport Association), igaragaza ko Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ari byo byari bifite umubare munini w'abagenzi bavuye i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari ahantu abantu benshi bahurira bavuye i Wuhan.
Bari yagaragaye ko ari yo ifite ikibazo cy'ubushobozi buke mu mijyi 20 ikenewe cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Australia yagaragaye ko ifite ubushobozi buke.
Hari amakuru menshi yagombaga kuvumburwa ku COVID-19, kandi Australia yagombaga guhanga amaso cyane imipaka yayo no guhangana na yo vuba.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko hari igihe cy'ikiruhuko cy'iza bukuru.
Kubera ko gahunda yo kwirinda ingendo z'abantu ku butaka bw'u Bushinwa yagize icyo igeraho mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uwa Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byakoze gahunda yo gukura abaturage n'abayobozi babo muri ako karere, kandi ibyo babikora binyuze mu ndege z'ubwubatsi z'abimukira bavuye muri icyo gihugu, babiherewe uburenganzira n'ubuyobozi bw'u Bushinwa.
Abategetsi ba mbere bateguye imigi y'ubuhungiro muri Kanada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, u Bufaransa, Arijantine, U Budage na Tayilande.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazongera kwirukana abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, igihugu cya Brezili cyahungaga abaturage bacyo 34 cyangwa imiryango imwe, kirwana n'abaturage bane b'Abaporotesitanti b'Abahindi.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhindi bavuye muri Polonye, aho indege y'indege ya Brazil yahagaze mbere y'uko igera muri Burezili.
Abaturage bo muri Brezili bari baraje i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato mu kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasília.
Ku munsi umwe, Abakanada 215 (176 bo mu ndege ya mbere, 39 bo mu ndege ya kabiri ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bajyanwa muri CFB Trenton mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari irimo Abakanada 185 yavuye i Wuhan ihagera muri CFB Trenton.
Ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi bo muri Ositaraliya baciye abaturage babo 277 mu kato, babajyana mu kigo cy'i Kirwa cya Noheli, aho bari barabategetse kumara iminsi 14 bari mu kato.
Indege yo muri Nouvelle-Zélande yari yahunze abantu bayo yageze i Auckland ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo n'abandi baturutse muri Ositaraliya no muri Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Amerika yatangaje ko yari guhunga Abanyamerika mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 bo muri Kanada yavuye muri Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, muri Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, leta y'u Buhinde yatangiye guhunga abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, leta ya Afurika y'Epfo, yafashe indege ya South African Airways guhunga abaturage bayo 112.
Ivuriro ryakozwe mbere y'uko indege ihaguruka kandi abaturage bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basiga inyuma kubera ko bari bafite ubwoba.
Abaturage bo muri Afurika y'Epfo batabayeho neza, ni bo basubijwe mu gihugu cyabo.
Ibisubizo by'ibyo biganiro byerekana ko abaturage bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bari muzima, barimo abakozi b'indege, abagenzi, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu gikorwa cyo gutanga imfashanyo, kandi bose bakomeje kugenzura mu buryo bwitondewe, bakamara iminsi 14 mu kato muri The Ranch Resort.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byari byatanze imfashanyo.
Abanyeshuri bakomoka mu Bushinwa biga muri Kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu bikorwa byo gufasha mu bice by'u Bushinwa byazahajwe n'icyorezo, ndetse n'umuryango wo mu mujyi wa Chicago wohereje ibinyabuzima 50,000 by'ubwoko bwa N95 ku bitaro byo mu mujyi wa Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama. Ishami ry'ubutabazi (The humanitarian aid organization Direct Relief) hamwe na FedEx, batanze ibinyabuzima 200,000 by'ubwoko bwa N95 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwoko bwabyo birimo igarabu na gauni, maze bajya mu ndege y'ubutabazi yihuta i Wuhan Union Hospital ku wa 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje inkunga ya miriyoni 100 z'amadolari ku kigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Gamije kugenzura imiti y'indwara n'imiti, ndetse no kurinda "abantu bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yahaye Filipinos ubwandu bwa kanseri 200,000 ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare nyuma y'aho Ambasaderi Richard Gordon ahereye i Wuhan akohereza ubwandu bwa kanseri miliyoni 3.16.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Umuryango Mpuzamahanga wita ku bantu bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona no kwicwa n'indwara (Cross Rouge) wo muri Singapuru, watangaje ko ugiye kohereza inkunga y'amadolari agera kuri miriyoni 2.26 mu Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze miliyoni imwe y'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, u Turukiya bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwatanze toni zisaga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko imaze guha u Bushinwa miliyoni 18 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Budage bwatanze toni 10.000 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birimo Hazmat suits, naho Amerika yahaye u Bushinwa toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi kandi igatanga icyizere cyo gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amafaranga yo gufasha ibihugu byibasiwe n'icyo cyorezo.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Ubushinwa, Chuba n'u Burusiya byoherereje ibikoresho byo kuvura n'abahanga mu gufasha u Butaliyani kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus cyari cyarabaye.
Umushoramari Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1, miliyoni 6 z'indwara za kanseri n'ibikoresho 60,000 i Addis Ababa, muri Etiyopiya, mu muryango w'ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Nyuma yaho yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, 100 000 by'ubwonko n'ibikoresho byo kuvura 5 muri Panama.
Ma yatanze ibikoresho byo kwivuza muri Kanada. Mu Buholandi, muri Esipanye, muri Turukiya, muri Jeworujiya no muri Repubulika ya Tchèque, hari abantu batangajwe n'uko hari ibikoresho byo gupima kanseri bikoreshwa mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yahagaritse ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus byakorewe mu Bushinwa, ariko ubuvuzi bwabyo bukaba ari 30% gusa, naho Ubuholandi buhagaritse ibikomere 600.000 by'ubwandu bwa coronavirus bwahitanye Ubushinwa.
U Bubiligi bwashyizeho ingirabuzimafatizo 100.000 zidashobora gukoreshwa, zitekereza ko zaturutse mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri zikava muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza cyane mu bihugu byo muri Amerika y'Epfo no muri Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije inkunga yihutirwa yo gufasha ibihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimiye cyane ibikorwa by'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
OMS yabonye itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyatangiye mu 2002-2004, ubwo abayobozi b'u Bushinwa basabwaga guceceka amabanga yabangamiye gahunda yo kwirinda no kurwanya icyorezo, n'ikibazo cy'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu "buri gihe buhamagarira abaturage kwirinda guhungabana mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya".
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza abayobozi ba leta ku cyemezo cyo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, umuvugizi wa OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo OMS itabivuze, byari igikorwa cyiza kandi kigaragaza ko yiyemeje kurwanya indwara mu gace gakunze gukwirakwizwa cyane, kandi ko cyari ikintu kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuvuzi. Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, ubwo guhanagurwa kw'abantu ku giti cyabo byari byemejwe hanze y'u Bushinwa kandi umubare w'abarwayi wiyongereye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cyari icyorezo cya kabiri ku isi cyari gikeneye kwitabwaho byihutirwa (Public Health Emergency of International Concern (PHEIC), cyatangajwe mu mwaka wa 2009, ubwo iki cyorezo cyasohokaga mu mwaka wa 2009.
Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima, yavuze ko iyi gahunda yo kwivuza mu bihugu by'ubukene "ibanze y'ikibazo cyugarije isi yose, cyane cyane ibihugu bifite amikoro make n'ibifite amikoro make.
Tedros yagize icyo avuga ku kibazo cy'ingendo, avuga ko "nta mpamvu n'imwe yatuma ingendo n'ubucuruzi byo ku isi bigira ingaruka nziza" kandi ko "OMS idashyigikira ko ingendo n'ubucuruzi bigabanuka".
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye abantu bo ku isi hose gutanga miriyoni 675 z'amadolari y'Amanyamerika kugira ngo bashyigikire ibikorwa byo gutegura ibihugu bifite ubwandu, ivuga ko byihutirwa gushyigikira ibyo bihugu "bitagira gahunda yo kuvura abantu banduye, mu gihe habayeho impanuka".
Tedros kandi yatangaje ko "imbaraga zacu zifite agaciro kenshi mu ntege nke zacu" kandi yasabye abantu bo hirya no hino ku isi "guhingira uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura byinshi ku munsi utaha".Ku wa 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari izina ry'iki cyorezo.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga wa Loni António Guterres yemeye gutanga "imbaraga zose za Loni mu kurwanya indwara".
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buryo bw'Ibibazo (UN Crisis Management Team) ryashyizweho kugira ngo rihuze n'ibikorwa by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, WHO ivuga ko bizatuma "ishyira imbere ubuvuzi nk'uko ibindi bigo by'umuryango w'abibumbye bibigira mu gihe bizaba bifasha mu bibazo by'imibereho myiza, ubukungu n'iterambere mu gihe cy'iki cyorezo".
Ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rihagarariwe mu Bushinwa ryashyizweho kugira ngo rijye mu Bushinwa riherereze impuguke z'isi yose n'iz'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) kugira ngo zifashe mu bikorwa byo gutabara mu ngo no mu gusuzuma "urugomo n'icyorezo cy'indwara" binyuze mu gutegura amasomo n'inama n'inzego z'ibanze mu gihugu no kujya mu bihugu byo mu karere "kugenzura ingaruka z'ibiza by'akarere n'ibya leta, harimo n'ibiza by'umujyi n'iby'intambara". Ku itariki ya 25 Gashyantare, umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) watangaje ko "isi igomba gukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo ikire gahunda yo kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus" ku isi, kandi ko nubwo igihe cyari kigeze guhita icyorezo cy'isi yose (pandemic), ibihugu byari bikomeje kuba "icyorezo".
Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba WHO bavuze ko ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya coronavirus ku rwego mpuzamahanga bugomba kwagurwa kuva ku "cyakomeye" bugashyirwa ku "cyakomeye cyane", ari nacyo cyiciro cya mbere cyo gusuzuma ikibazo.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi w'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) mu rwego rw'ubukungu, yatanze umuburo agira ati "iki ni ikintu cyagombye gushakirwa buri butegetsi ku isi: nimukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira igana, kandi mukeneye kuba mwiteguye", kandi ndababwira ko kugira uburyo bwiza bwo kuyirwanya bishobora gutuma isi ireka "icyorezo gikomeye".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru y'ubu atari yo yatumye abayobozi b'ubuzima batangaza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cy'isi yose, avuga ko gutangaza ibintu nk'ibyo byari kuba bisobanura ko "twemera ko abantu bose ku isi bazandura".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko coronavirus ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko "yari ifite impungenge z'uko virusi ikomeza kugenda yihuta cyane, ko nta cyo ikora". OMS yarashenguwe n'uko nta cyo ikora ku buryo ikwirakwiza indwara, harimo gutinda gutangaza ko hari ikibazo cy'ubuzima gihangayikishije kandi ko ari icy'isi yose.
Muri iyo myigaragambyo harimo no guhata Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom ngo ahagarike, ubwo gahunda yashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 ubwo yatangiraga ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere za ONU zivuga ku burenganzira bwa muntu zashyigikiye ko uburenganzira bwa muntu buhabwa agaciro mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y'u Rwanda yavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kubona ibyokurya bidakiza ubuzima kandi ko ari inshingano ya leta.
Iri tsinda ryemeje ko kubura ibikoresho cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bitazagombye gufatwa nk'ikinyoma cy'urwikekwe.
Abahanga mu by'ubuvuzi bemeje ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, hakubiyemo abafite ubumuga, amatsinda mato, abasaza, abafite impunzi, abatagira aho baba, abafite ibibazo bikomeye, imfungwa, impunzi n'abandi bose bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Ibigo bya leta ku isi hose bigira uruhare mu guhangana n'ikibazo cya COVID-19 ku bukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Bufatanye mu by'Igihugu n'Iterambere ryashyizeho uburyo bwo gutanga amakuru y'igihe kandi yuzuye ku mikorere yashyizweho n'ibihugu byo hirya no hino ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'ubwenge.
Kuva ku bikorwa byo gushyigikira ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi kugeza ku bikorwa byo kurwanya ingendo n'imfungwa, uburyo bumwe ni Country Policy Tracker, kandi bugamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga hakiri kare no guhuza ibikorwa mpuzamahanga mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yahagurukijwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bwongereza Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro Eduardo Bolsonaro kubera uburyo bakemuye iki kibazo, cyatangiye mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi benshi b'Intara mu ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'u Bushinwa (CPC) birukanwe kubera uburyo bakoreshaga gahunda yo kwirinda icyorezo mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, bikaba bigaragaza ko batishimiye uko abayobozi bakoreshaga iyo ndwara.
Bamwe mu barebye ibibera muri iki gihugu bavuga ko icyo gikorwa cyabaye mu rwego rwo gukiza umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
