Abashinwa n'abandi baturage bo muri Aziya bo mu Bwongereza no muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, bavuga ko ibikorwa byo kwicira urubanza, ivangura n'ihohoterwa byongereye.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Gurdwaras, yarashenguwe cyane no kwita coronavirus "Virus of China", ijambo abarwanya ubutegetsi b'u Bushinwa bitaga ko ari urwikekwe kandi ko ari urwango ku Bushinwa.
Imyigaragambyo yo muri Ukraine yagabye igitero ku bisi yari itwaye abaturage bo muri Ukraine n'abanyamahanga i Wuhan ibajyana i Sanzhary.
Abanyeshuri bo mu majyaruguru ashyira uburasirazuba bw'u Buhinde, ubu buhuriye n'u Bushinwa, biga mu mijyi minini yo mu Buhinde bivugwa ko bahanganye n'ikibazo cy'uburwayi bwa coronavirus.
Perezida wa leta ya Bengali y'Iburengerazuba, mu ishyaka ry'Abaharatiya Janata Party, Dilip Ghosh, yavuze ko Abashinwa bonona ibidukikije, "ni cyo cyatumye Imana ibahana".
Ayo magambo yaje kuvugwaho rumwe n'intumwa y'u Bushinwa i Kolkata, ikavuga ko ari "ibyaha".Mu Bushinwa, urwango rw'abanyamahanga n'ivangura rishingiye ku moko ku baturage batari Abashinwa byatewe n'iki cyorezo, aho abanyamahanga bita "umwanda w'abanyamahanga" kandi bakagenzura "kumuterera".
Ibinyamakuru byinshi bifite ibigo by'abanyamakuru byakuyeho amakuru y'icyorezo cya coronavirus mu bice bimwe cyangwa byose.
