Igerageza ry'ubwandu bwa coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) hamwe n'umugera utera SARS-CoV-2 rigizwe n'uburyo bwo gupima virusi na antibody bikora igihe umuntu arwaye virusi.
Kugira virusi mu bipimo by'ubwandu byemezwa na RT-PCR, ikora ubushakashatsi kuri RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki kigeragezo cyakozwe mu rwego rwo gupima RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 gusa.
Iyo virusi ikoreshwa mu kwirinda ko umuntu yanduzwa cyangwa ngo igire icyo ikora.
Igishushanyo cy'ubwonko (serology) gishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima indwara cyangwa kumenya umubare w'abanduye.
Iyo bagerageje gusuzuma abarwayi, baba basanze abantu bafite ibimenyetso by'iyo ndwara ari bake cyane ku buryo batagombaga kujya kwa muganga cyangwa batagaragaje ibimenyetso.
Umubare nyawo w'abapfuye n'imimerere abantu barimo bashobora guhura na yo, bishobora kumenyekana binyuze muri ubu bushakashatsi.
Kubera ko ibipimo by'ubwandu bisigaye bidahagije, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020 nta gihugu na kimwe cyabonye amakuru y'ukuri y'uko virusi itera mu baturage bacyo.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigenzura abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi umubare w'abantu bagenzurwa ku isi hose wari utandukanye cyane.
Ibyo bishobora gutuma umubare w'abarwayi bapfa uhinduka, bikaba bishobora kuba byarazamutse cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Gukoresha uburyo bwo guhinduranya imikorere ya transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) mu gihe nyacyo, ibipimo by'imyanya ndangagitsina bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'imyanya ndangagitsina bibonerwa mu buryo butandukanye, harimo gukoreshwa kw'imyanya ndangagitsina mu mazuru no mu mazuru cyangwa ku bipimo by'imyanya ndangagitsina.
Ingaruka rusange zitangwa mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Igerageza rya RT-PCR rigizwe n'ibipimo by'ubwonko n'ibikomoka ku mubiri ni ryo ryizerwa cyane kuko ryakorewe mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma yaho, iyo virusi ishobora gutembera mu maraso, nk'uko bigenda mu mahaha.
Mu barwayi bageragejwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ibipimo by'ibipimo bishobora gukurwa mu nzira z'umuriro bikoresheje ikinyabiziga (suction catheter) cyangwa se ikinyabiziga.
Kimwe mu byiciro bya mbere bya PCR byakozwe mu kigo cy'ubuvuzi cya Charité i Berlin mu kwezi kwa kabiri 2020 hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rya rRT-PCR (real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction), ari nacyo cyatumye hakorwa ibipimo 250,000 byatanzwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza na bwo bwari bwateye imbere uburyo bwo gupima ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebiotech cyatangije ikigeragezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku itariki ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Igerageza gushaka urumuri "E" rw'ubwoko bwose bwa coronavirus beta, ndetse n'urw'ubwoko RdRp rw'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 gusa.Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni imwe mu bigo bya mbere byemerewe byihuse na National Medical Products Administration y'u Bushinwa gukoresha ikigeragezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR.Mu gihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibigo by'ubuvuzi n'ubutabazi (CDC) byatanze ikigeragezo cya RT 2019-Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) cya Real-Time-PCR Diagnostic Panel ku biganiro bya leta binyuze muri International Reagent Resource.
Imwe mu myitozo itatu y'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima ikoreshwa mu gukora ibizamini bya kera yagaragaje ko ibizamini by'ibinyabuzima bitagira iherezo biterwa n'ibiyobyabwenge bidakora neza (faulty reagents), ndetse n'ibibazo byo gupima ku kigo cya CDC kiri i Atlanta; byatumye ibizamini bitarenga 100 ku munsi biba bikiriho kugeza mu kwezi kwa kabiri 2020.
Gusuzuma uburyo bubiri ntibyari byemewe kugeza ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi kugeza icyo gihe, ibyangombwa bya leta n'iby'ibihugu by'amahanga ntibyari byemewe gutangira gusuzuma.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ubuyobozi bw'ibiyobyabwenge n'ibiribwa mu rwego rw'ubugenzuzi bw'ibanze bw'igihugu (FDA) mu gihe cy'itegeko ry'ubugenzuzi bw'ibanze (Emergence Use Authorization).
Ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe 2020 LabCorp yatangaje ko ibizamini bya COVID-19 byakozwe mu gihugu hose bishingiye kuri RT-PCR.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, Quest Diagnostics yatumye ibizamini bya COVID-19 byashobora gukwirakwira mu gihugu hose igihe byatangiraga ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta gipimo gihari; gukusanya ibizamini no kubikurikiza bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibyo CDC isaba.
Mu Burusiya, ibipimo bya COVID-19 byateguwe kandi byasohotse n'Ikigo cya Leta cy'Ubushakashatsi mu Binyabuzima na Virology VECTOR.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 iki gikoresho cyo gupima cyasabwe na Federal Service for Surveillance in Healthcare.Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yateye imbere ikigeragezo cya COVID-19.Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rw'ikigeragezo gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3.5 gusa, bigatuma ikikoresho kimwe gishobora gupima abantu bagera kuri 4.128 mu masaha 24.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yahaye uruhushya rw'ihutirwa Laboratwari za Abbott kugira ngo zigerageze uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga rya Abbott m2000; FDA yari imaze guha uruhushya rw'ibanze Hologic, LabCorp na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid na yo yahawe uruhushya byihuse na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini cy'iminota 45.
FDA yemeje ko ikoranabuhanga ryo kongera ingufu za nucleic acid isothermal risimbura PCR.
Kubera ko iyo nzira idakeneye guhindurwa mu bushyuhe, ishobora gutanga ibimenyetso byerekana ko umuntu afite virusi mu minota itanu gusa, naho ikerekana ko nta ndwara y'ibicurane afite mu minota 13.
Ubu hari ibi bikoresho bigera ku 18,000 muri Amerika kandi Abbott yifuza ko bizongera mu gukora ibizamini byo gupima abantu 50,000 ku munsi.Ibizamini bikoresha antibody ya monoclonal nk'iyi bihuza na protini ya nucleocapsid (N protein) yanduye coronavirus nshya iri gukorwa muri Taiwan, byitezwe ko ishobora gutanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza 20 nk'uko byagenze mu gupima icyorezo cya Gishyu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Werurwe 2020 bwagaragaje ko "imibonano mpuzabitsina yo mu gituza nta cyo imaze mu bihe bya mbere, kandi ko ibimenyetso by'iyo miti bishobora kuba bitaragaragara".
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara muri CT ni ibipimo bya opacificities bya gilasi y'ibirahuri bya bilateral multilobar hamwe n'ibipimo bya peripheral, asymmetric na posterior distribution.
Ubutegetsi bw'ibikomere, kurema ibishya no gushikama biragenda birushaho gukomera uko indwara zinyura mu mibiri.
Ubushakashatsi bugereranya PCR na CT i Wuhan mu gace k'icyorezo cyatangiye bwagaragaje ko CT ikora vuba kurusha PCR, nubwo ititabwaho cyane, kuko amashusho menshi yayo atuma umuntu atakaza ubwonko n'izindi ndwara.
Muri Werurwe 2020, American College of Radiology yatanze inama igira iti "CT ntiyagombye gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa gukora ibizamini bya mbere bya COVID-19".
