Ibice by'akazi bibangamiwe na COVID-19
Ingamba zo kwirinda impanuka n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni zo z'ingenzi cyane mu guhangana n'ibibazo by'akazi byatewe na COVID-19.
Uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda akaga k'akazi buva ku mwanya w'akazi n'aho kazi gakorerwa, kandi ibyo bigerageza guhangana n'imbuto z'iki cyorezo, uburemere bw'iki cyorezo mu karere, n'akaga k'abakozi bashobora guhura na COVID-19.
Dukurikije ibivugwa n'ikigo gishinzwe umutekano mu kazi n'ubuzima muri Amerika (OSHA), imirimo ifite ibyago bike cyane, ifitanye isano n'akazi n'abandi bakozi, kandi ishobora gukemuka binyuze mu gukoresha uburyo buke bwo kwivuza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gushyira mu bikorwa amahame agenga uburyo bwo guhumeka, no guhora bakora mu buryo buzira ubwikunde mu kazi.
Imirimo itoroshye cyane ni iyo abantu bahuriye cyane n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura kubera ko icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu karere cyangwa kubera ko bagiye mu mahanga.
Muri ibyo bintu hakubiyemo abakozi bafatanyije n'abandi, urugero nk'amashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo imirimo n'amaduka.
Kugira ngo abantu bakomeze kwirinda ibyo byorezo, bagomba gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda indwara, harimo gukoresha imyanda ihumeka neza, no kwambara imyenda ikingira umubiri mu gihe hari umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ikora ku baganga/abaforomo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi ku bantu bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19 kuko bafite ibyago byinshi, kandi ibyo bigatuma ibyago bikomera cyane iyo abo bakozi bafashe ibipimo by'umubiri w'umuntu wapfuye cyangwa ukekwaho kuba yapfuye COVID-19.
Mu byo aba bakozi bakora harimo uburyo bwo kubaka, urugero nko gukingira umwuka kuva mu cyumba ujya mu kindi, no gukora imyitozo ngororamubiri ikwiriye.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora gutuma ibikorwa by'akazi bigira ingaruka nyinshi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batarabona akazi kubera uburwayi, ko bakeneye kwita ku bandi, cyangwa se kubera ko batinya ko bashobora kurwara.
Ubucuruzi bushobora guhinduka bitewe n'ibyo abantu bifuza n'uburyo bagura ibyo bintu (urugero nko kugura mu gihe cy'ibihe bidasanzwe ku isoko cyangwa gushaka kubagezaho ibyo bakeneye cyangwa kuba ahantu hatandukanye n'aho imodoka ziri).
Icya nyuma, ingendo z'ibicuruzwa ziva mu duce twugarijwe na COVID-19 zishobora guhungabana. Gutegura icyorezo cyandura n'uburyo bwo kucyirwanya birakenewe kugira ngo bigire uruhare mu kuyobora ibikorwa by'ubwigenge.
Imishinga ireba ibipimo by'akaga bigendana n'aho ikorerwa ndetse n'akazi ako ari ko kose, harimo ingaruka z'ubwandu, ingaruka zo mu rugo no mu karere, n'izindi ngaruka z'uburwayi ziterwa n'imyaka cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Bashyizeho amategeko agenga ibyo kwirinda, n'ingamba zo kwirinda indwara z'ibyorezo.
Gutegura indwara zishobora gutuma igihugu cyose cyangwa akarere kose gakira icyo gukoza.
Intego zo kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'ibiza zirimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byo kurwara indwara ziterwa n'ibibazo bikomeye, gukomeza ibikorwa, no kugabanya ingaruka ku bakozi bakorana mu gihe cy'umurimo wabo.
Indwara z'ibyorezo mu gace k'ubucuruzi zagiye zigira ingaruka ku buryo bwo kuzirwanya.
Ingamba zo kurwanya ibibazo ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane ku isi mu guhangana n'ibibazo by'akazi n'ubuzima binyuriye mu gusenya uburyo bukoreshwa mu rwego rwo kwita ku buzima.
Iyo ikibazo cya COVID-19 kitakemuka, kwirinda birenze ubushobozi bwacyo bwo gucunga ingufu (engineering controls), aho gukoresha uburyo bw'ubuyobozi (administrative controls) n'uburyo bwo gutangiza umuntu ku giti cye.
Ingengabihe y'ubuhinzi irimo gukura abakozi mu bibazo by'akazi mu buryo budahuje n'imyifatire y'akazi kandi akenshi usanga ari bwo buryo bworoshye bwo gushyira mu bikorwa.
