Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutorwa hakurikijwe ibyago umukoresha ashobora guhura na byo, bugomba gushyirwa ahantu hakwiriye gushyirwaho kandi hakwiye kurindwa (ni ukuvuga mu gihe cy'ubugenzuzi), bugomba kwambara igihe cyose kandi mu buryo bwiza, bugakorwa igenzura buri gihe, bukagenerwa kwitabwaho, bugakoreshwa mu kugarura ibyago, bugomba gukurwaho neza uko bikenewe, bugakorwaho ubuvugizi, bukagenerwa kubika cyangwa bukaturwaho mu rwego rwo kwirinda indwara.
Dukurikije ibivugwa n'ikigo gishinzwe umutekano mu kazi n'ubuzima muri Amerika (OSHA), imirimo itari iy'ingorabahizi cyane, ni ugukorana n'abantu badafite aho bahuriye n'abandi bakozi.
