Muri ibyo bikorwa harimo guhuza abakozi n'abandi, urugero nk'amashuri, ibigo by'akazi by'abantu benshi, n'amaduka yuzuye. Gukurikirana inganda (Engineering controls) muri ibi bigo n'ibigo by'abakora ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi birimo gushyiraho inganda z'umwuka mu nzu, kongera inganda z'ibisasu, gushyiraho inganda z'ubushakashatsi z'abantu benshi, no gushyiraho amadirishya y'ibyangombwa by'imashini. Gukurikirana inganda z'abakora imirimo y'ubushakashatsi (Administrative controls) muri ibi bigo birimo ibibazo by'ubushakashatsi, bigiraho gushyiraho inganda z'imyenda iteza imbere inganda z'ubwubatsi, kongera inganda z'ubwubatsi, gushyiraho inganda z'ubwubatsi z'ibyangombwa by'ubwubatsi, gushyiraho inganda z'ubwubatsi mu gihe cy'ubwubatsi, gushyiraho inganda z'ubwubatsi, gushyiraho imihati n'amabwiriza, gushishinga abakozi, gushishikariza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi, gushyiraho ibikoresho byo guhangana n'ubushakashatsi, gushyiraho imihati, gushyiraho imihati ku mugaragaro ibipimo, gushyiraho ibipimo by'ubwubatsi, gushyiraho, gushyiraho ibipimo by'ubwubatsi, gushyiraho, gushyiraho ibipimo by'ubwubatsi, gushyiraho, gushyiraho neza, gushyiraho ibipimo, gushyiraho ibipimo, gushyiraho kandi gushyiraho ibipimo, gushyiraho ibipimo, gushyiraho ibipimo, gushyiraho ibisobanuro, gushyiraho ibisobanuro, gushyiraho ibisobanuro, gushyiraho ibisobanuro, n'ibikoreshwa mu bikorwa.
