Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzima fatizo y'umubiri (ku mubiri w'umuntu) ifata imyanya ndangagitsina mu ngingo, mu ngingo, mu mutima, mu gitsina, n'ibindi.
ACE2 itera ingufu za angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II igafata ingano ya Ang(1-7) igatuma ikoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora nk'inkomoko y'indwara zimwe na zimwe za coronavirus.
Mu bantu, icyo cyorezo cyitwa hACE2.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 irimo zinc irimo metalloenzyme iboneka ku gice cyo hejuru cy'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso n'izindi ngirabuzimafatizo.
Poroteyine ACE2 ifite N-terminal peptidase M2 domain na C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 igera ku ruhu rw'umubiri rimwe, aho ibirungo byayo by'ibanze bigaragara ku gice cyo hejuru cy'ibishyimbo mu bice by'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Icyiciro cya ACE2 cy'ubundi bwoko cyakuwe mu mubiri, gigahindurwa sheddase, maze amazi avamo poroteyine agashyirwamo mu maraso, hanyuma agahindurwa umunyu.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifata uruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo cyane cyane iz'ubwoko bwa II z'ibinyabuzima by'umubiri, uruhu rw'ibinyabuzima, imitsi n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso, n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
Igiterwa cy'ubwonko (ACE2 mRNA) kiboneka no mu bice by'umubiri bigera mu bwonko, mu bwonko, mu bwonko bw'ibere no mu gice cy'ibere.
Icy'ingenzi cyane cya ACE2 ni ugusubizaho ACE
ACE ifata ingufu za angiotensin I mu myitozo igena angiotensin II.
ACE2 ikorana na carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine iva kuri angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayihindura angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no gukora ku migenzereze itandukanye, urugero nka [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 nayo igenzura ingendo z'uruhu zigana kuri SLC6A19 ifite amino acid idasesuye kandi bivugwa ko ari yo ituma indwara ya Hartnup iba.
Iyo poroteyine igenda mu ruhu, ACE2 ikora nk'irembo rikuru ry'inyuma y'ibinyabuzima byanduye virusi zimwe na zimwe za corona, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhura kw'ibinyabuzima bya spike S1 bya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ku cyuma cy'ingenzi cya ACE2 ku gice cyo hejuru cy'ibinyabuzima bituma virusi n'ibinyabuzima biva aho biri bigasubira mu cyuma cy'ibinyabuzima.
Iyi gahunda yo kwinjira kandi igomba guhitamo poroteyine ya S hamwe na serine protease TMPRSS2, aho igenewe mu gihe cy'ubugenzuzi bw'ubuvuzi. Ibi byatumye bamwe batekereza ko iyo igabanya umubare wa ACE2, mu ngirabuzimafatizo, ishobora gufasha kurwanya indwara.
Ahubwo, inzego z'ubuvuzi n'izindi nzego z'ubuyobozi zemeza ko ACE inhibitor izwi cyane ikoreshwa mu kuvura ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga mu by'indwara z'igituntu bwakozwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko "kwifashisha imiti ihagarika ACE byagabanyije ubukana bw'igituntu ku kigero cya 34 ku ijana kurusha ubundi buryo bwo kuvura igituntu
Mu by'ukuri, "ibipimo by'ubwandu bw'indwara ya malariya byagabanutse mu barwayi bahabwa imiti ihagarika ingufu za ACE, cyane cyane mu barwayi b'umutima
Gukoresha imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara ya ACE byatekerejwe ko byagabanya urupfu rw'abantu bapfa bazize ibicurane, nubwo nta ngaruka mbi cyane byagize"
Recombinant human ACE2 (rhACE2) bivugwa ko ari umuti wihariye wo kurwara indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero bw'ibihaha, kandi wagaragaye ko ushobora kuzamura imikorere y'ibihaha n'imyuka y'umwuka mu bice by'umubiri by'ibinyabuzima by'ibihaha byanduye indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'ibihaha biterwa na lipopolysaccharide.
Kugabanya rhACE2 mu bantu bifata amasaha 10 kandi ibikorwa byatangira mu minota 30, nubwo byamaze amasaha 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu buryo butandukanye bugaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti utera icyizere ku bantu badahangana n'ibibuguza imikorere ya renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa ku barwayi bafite ingendo za angiotensin II zifite imbaraga.Infused rhACE2 irimo igeragezwa mu buvuzi mu kuvura indwara z'amaraso.
