Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple batangaje ko bagiye gufatanya gushyigikira porogaramu nka Bluetooth kuri Android na iOS mu buryo butaziguye mu mikoranire yabo.
Mu Bushinwa, Leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipau, yashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bayo basuzuma niba barwaye COVID-19.
Mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa, ikoreshwa muri Singapuru, ikoranabuhanga rya TraceTogether.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'abahanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga bo mu karere, yasohotse ku buntu kandi izahabwa inkunga na leta. Macedonia ya Ruguru yatangije porogaramu ya Bluetooth "StopKorona!", igamije gukurikirana abitabiriye n'abari ku rwego rw'ubuzima n'abategetsi.
Porogaramu y'iyi porogaramu yashyizweho na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho na Tekoroji hamwe na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu izaba yemewe na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku itariki ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abanduye iri mu cyiciro cya nyuma cyo gukorwa, ikaba izaba itangiye gukora mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyo iri gukorwa muri Irilande, no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na New Zealand birimo gutekereza kuri TraceTogether app ya Singapore na protocol ya BlueTrace.Russia iri gutegura gushyiraho app ya geofencing y'abanduye COVID-19 baba i Moscow, igamije guhora itegereje ko batava mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ko hari ibibazo by'ikoranabuhanga rishingiye kuri porogaramu, harimo ko iyo porogaramu ikoreshwa n'abantu benshi ishobora gukora neza cyangwa ikabura gukora neza.
Kugira ngo Apple ikemure ibibazo by'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga bibangamira cyangwa bibangamiye, yashyizeho ibihano ku mibare y'ibigo byashobora gushyira porogaramu zifite isano na coronavirus muri App Store, yemera gusa ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga cyangwa ibigo bizwi.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
